update.name: WordPress-Auto-Admin-Account-and-Reverse-Shell-cve-2024-27956
update.description: WordPress Auto Admin Account Creation and Reverse Shell cve-2024-27956 automates the process of creating a new administrator account in a WordPress site and executing a reverse shell on the target server. It utilizes the wp-automatic plugin's CSV injection vulnerability to execute SQL queries
